SIMPLE: intervene
RECORDS: 3

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Intervene
<hw>In`ter*vene"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp.
& p. p.</pos> <conjf>Intervened</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
n.</pos> <conjf>Intervening</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[L.
<ets>intervenire</ets>, <ets>interventum</ets>, to intervene, to hinder;
<ets>inter</ets> between + <ets>venire</ets> to come; akin to E.
<ets>come</ets>: cf. F. <ets>intervenir</ets>. See
<er>Come</er>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>To come between, or to be between, persons or
things; -- followed by <xex>between</xex>; <as>as, the Mediterranean
<ex>intervenes</ex> between Europe and Africa</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To occur, fall, or come between, points of time, or
events; <as>as, an instant <ex>intervened</ex> between the flash and the
report; nothing <ex>intervened</ex> ( <it>i. e.</it>, between the
intention and the execution) to prevent the undertaking.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>To interpose; <as>as, to <ex>intervene</ex> to
settle a quarrel</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>4.</sn> <def>In a suit to which one has not been made a party, to
put forward a defense of one's interest in the subject matter.</def>
<rj><au>Abbott.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Intervene</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Intervene
<hw>In`ter*vene"</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To come between.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Self-sown woodlands of birch, alder, etc., <qex>intervening</qex>
the different estates.</q> <rj><qau>De Quincey.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Intervene</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Intervene
<hw>In`ter*vene"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A coming between;
intervention; meeting.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Sir H.
Wotton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Intervener</ent>⟦br⟧
